        "timestamp": "2019-12-04 18:23:48.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Jorge, could you guide me how to change values.yaml to make this\n > new config apply to only snapshot version?\n\nYep, just one line change in kubernetes/policy/charts/policy-api/values.yaml (see the diff below):\n\ndiff --git a/kubernetes/policy/charts/policy-api/values.yaml b/kubernetes/policy/charts/policy-api/values.yaml\nindex 3a55227d..193a0dea 100644\n--- a/kubernetes/policy/charts/policy-api/values.yaml\n+++ b/kubernetes/policy/charts/policy-api/values.yaml\n@@ -28,7 +28,7 @@ global:\n #################################################################\n # application image\n repository: nexus3.onap.org:10001\n-image: onap/policy-api:2.1.2\n+image: onap/policy-api:2.2-SNAPSHOT-latest\n pullPolicy: Always\n \n # flag to enable debugging - application support required",
